response.doc:
200 ok {"result":"cmd> server listn ivmgrd-mastern test-webseald-appliance"}
Note: HTTP response code and JSON data that represents the output from the pdadmin commands. If you run multiple pdadmin commands, a failure response is only returned if the last command fails. If a command other than the last fails, the response is successful. View the result to ensure that the previous commands are all successful. Also, if a single command fails, it does not halt the operation of subsequent commands.
Note: This API takes into account whether or not the machine it is running on is a Cluster Restricted Node. If it is a Cluster Restricted Node, the API will only work if the requester is the same host machine.
